---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Band from '../components/Band.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Isaiah Ho — business student at Singapore Management University, building toward strategy and management consulting."
>
  <Band variant="ink" eyebrow="01 — About">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <div class="prose">
      {/* TODO(isaiah): replace this placeholder bio with your real one. Only
          known facts were used here (SMU business student, targeting
          strategy/management consulting) — no specific achievements, GPA,
          clubs, internships, or awards have been invented. Add those yourself. */}
      <p class="lede">
        I'm Isaiah Ho, a business student at Singapore Management University
        (SMU), currently working toward a career in strategy and management
        consulting.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm drawn to problems that reward structured thinking: breaking down
        an ambiguous question, testing a hypothesis against evidence, and
        landing on a recommendation someone can actually act on. That's the
        thread running through the case work, research, and projects on this
        site.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of coursework, I'm building the habit of writing things down
        — partly to think more clearly, partly so there's a record of how my
        thinking changes over time. This site is that record.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Band>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .prose {
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #c9ccd9;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin: 0 0 1.2rem;
  }
</style>
